Showing Databases
-----------------
-To lists all available databases
Sql- show databases; 

Creating Database
-----------------
-Creates a database with the specified name
Sql- create database <database-name>; 
     create database if not exists <database-name>; 

Deleting Database
-----------------
-Deletes an entire database
Sql- drop database <database-name>; 
     drop database if exists <database-name>; 

Using Database
--------------
-Sets the specified database as the current working database for subsequent SQL commands.
Sql- use <database-name>; 

Showing Current Working Database
---------------------------------
-Returns the name of the database that is currently selected
Sql- SELECT database(); 



